      "title": "Four fuel shipments to reach SL this month",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four fuel shipments including three diesel shipments are expected to arrive in Sri Lanka this month, Power and Energy Minister Kanchana Wijesekara said.",
        "Addressing a media briefing, the minister said diesel shipments will reach Sri Lanka July 8th - 9th, July 11th-14th and the third shipment on July 15-17.",
        "He said the Petrol shipment will reach Sri Lanka on July 22-23."
      ],
